-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Theme Previewer - An interactive dijit theme showcase.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Authors: Bill Keese et al (copied here as a demo by Doug Hays)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Demo description

	This demo creates examples of all dijit widgets using the claro theme by default.
	The theme can be switched to alternate themes of tundra and soria, common to older Dojo releases.
	The default layout direction can also be changed from left-to-right to right-to-left.
	A simulated high-contrast (a11y) mode is available as well.
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

	Dojo Core
	dijit

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions

	Run the included demo.html
		
